{"data":[{"name":"113:1","price":"1. (நபியே! நீர் பிரார்த்தனை செய்து) கூறுவீராக அதிகாலையின் இறைவனிடம், நான் பாதுகாப்பைக் கோருகிறேன்.","arabic":"قُلۡ أَعُوذُ بِرَبِّ ٱلۡفَلَقِ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6226,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"qul aʿūdhu birabbi al-falaqi ","translations":["Say","I seek refuge","in (the) Lord","(of) the dawn","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["qul","aʿūdhu","birabbi","al-falaqi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,360],[2,360,1280],[3,1280,2110],[4,2110,3005]]}},{"name":"113:2","price":"2. அவன் படைத்திருக்கும் பொருள்களின் தீங்கை விட்டும்,","arabic":"مِن شَرِّ مَا خَلَقَ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6227,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"min sharri mā khalaqa ","translations":["From","(the) evil","(of) what","He created","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["min","sharri","mā","khalaqa",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,940],[2,940,2040],[3,2040,2380],[4,2380,3595]]}},{"name":"113:3","price":"3. (அனைத்தையும்) மறைத்துக் கொள்ளும் இருண்ட இருளின் தீங்கை விட்டும்,","arabic":"وَمِن شَرِّ غَاسِقٍ إِذَا وَقَبَ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6228,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wamin sharri ghāsiqin idhā waqaba ","translations":["And from","(the) evil","(of) darkness","when","it spreads","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wamin","sharri","ghāsiqin","idhā","waqaba",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,740],[2,740,2140],[3,2140,3250],[4,3250,3870],[5,3870,4945]]}},{"name":"113:4","price":"4. முடிச்சுப் போட்டு ஊதும் (சூதுக்கார) பெண்களின் தீங்கைவிட்டும்,","arabic":"وَمِن شَرِّ ٱلنَّفَّٰثَٰتِ فِي ٱلۡعُقَدِ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6229,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wamin sharri al-nafāthāti fī al-ʿuqadi ","translations":["And from","(the) evil","(of) the blowers","in","the